comments.body:
The cause of this bug are following lines

{code}
    fs.setTimes(FROM, MODIFICATION_TIME, ACCESS_TIME);
    fs.setPermission(FROM, PERMISSIONS);
    fs.setTimes(DIR_FROM, MODIFICATION_TIME, ACCESS_TIME);
    fs.setPermission(DIR_FROM, PERMISSIONS);
{code}

Setting permissions after setting the access and modification time will reset these times, Hence these events needs to be re-ordered.
